{"tid":1758612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(推上熱門比民陣睇）民陣幾時先肯再搞遊行","createTime":"2019-11-27T07:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T10:42:25.000Z","uid":58803,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"96eca21dfa896692f377df4d17fba8049848b493","tid":1758612,"uid":58803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:04:41.000Z","msg":"我等唔切啦<br />\n我要200萬人遊行啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主題乜都好啦<br />\n同柒婆重新五大訴求<br />\n聲援理工中大手足<br />\n追究721 831 101 <br />\n追究警隊強姦案<br />\n追究警隊濫權<br />\n追究1118 油麻地警車沖入人群導致人踩人<br />\n<br />\n贏左個小小區選，係開心既<br />\n但我地係咪可以唔再追究之前所發生既事？<br />\n大家係咪唔記得班狗之前d 咀臉？唔記得佢地點對我地手足？<br />\n<br />\n而家街邊d road block 已經清哂，無左既磚頭已經鋪返石屎，文宣都比人清哂，紅隧通返，就好似之前發生既所有事都係一場夢咁。<br />\n<br />\n香港人一向係善忙既，如果我地唔不斷提住大家，呢d 事就會繼續慢慢淡化。<br />\n<br />\n求下大家keep 住前五個幾月既憤怒，話比正苦知，香港人never forget, never forgive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a210926468b95575e30fe8b8ab4d4efd264f2f","tid":1758612,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:04:54.000Z","msg":"呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，<br />\n以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1756593/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1756593/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1mLv7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1mLv7K.jpg&h=e3eb5407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZTgSVzr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZTgSVzr.jpg&h=ebd5ef32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9107740d0835dc9ce99c8b25c2551f9c36d28c5b","tid":1758612,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/